         <abstract id="aspace_bf1dc7bb386851e866ed52b012bd4d14">The collection consists of correspondence, blotters, bills, daybooks, and legal papers of the Smith and Hine Company, a general store in Warren, Connecticut. The material mainly concerns the sale of groceries and dry goods.</abstract>
